## 8. Complete API Reference

### Direct Queries (Flutter → PostgREST)

| Method | Endpoint | Screen |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/rest/v1/task_catalog` | Task Picker |
| `GET` | `/rest/v1/v_user_dashboard?user_id=eq.{uid}` | Home Dashboard |
| `GET` | `/rest/v1/users?uid=eq.{uid}` | Profile |
| `POST` | `/rest/v1/user_tasks` | Task Picker |
| `PATCH` | `/rest/v1/users?uid=eq.{uid}` | Character Creation |
| `GET` | `/rest/v1/user_inventory?user_id=eq.{uid}` | Coin Shop |
| `GET` | `/rest/v1/user_achievements?user_id=eq.{uid}` | Profile |
| `GET` | `/rest/v1/neighborhoods?id=eq.{id}` | Neighborhood |
| `GET` | `/rest/v1/raid_bosses?neighborhood_id=eq.{id}&is_active=eq.true` | Neighborhood |
| `GET` | `/rest/v1/v_city_buildings?city_plot_x=...` | Unity 3D |

### Edge Functions (validated server-side)

| Function | Screen | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `complete-task` | Task Detail | Validate + earn + update |
| `recover-streak` | Streak Recovery | Pay coins + restore |
| `get-leaderboard` | Leaderboard | Redis sorted set read |
| `purchase-item` | Coin Shop | Atomic purchase |
| `get-city-data` | Unity 3D | Nearby plots |
| `buy-streak-shield` | Streak screen | Shield purchase |
| `join-neighborhood` | Neighborhood | Dual membership enforcement |
| `found-neighborhood` | Profile (Lv10+) | Create neighborhood |

### Realtime Subscriptions

| Table | Screen | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `streaks` (own rows) | Home Dashboard | Live streak count |
| `raid_bosses` | Neighborhood | Raid progress |
| `users` (own row) | All | Status/coins/level changes |

